{"tid":1708543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望啲人唔好咁做啦","createTime":"2019-11-11T15:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T15:28:12.000Z","uid":325482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"79d2f4c3ec34d6a63d89b497efc43ef946b72fe1","tid":1708543,"uid":325482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"一：攪㝝巴士：噴漆或用油漆彈整個大銀幕（其實油漆彈可以用雞蛋 用針筒抽晒蛋液 再入油漆）<br />\n二：落釘係馬路 但真係唔好喺公路 可以係喺市區入面馬路又安全收效又大<br />\n三：黨鐵電欖 範圍大 防不勝防<br />\n三樣嘢做齊 一個禮拜 香港即㝝 拉到都係刑毀 成本小 收效大<br />\n真心唔好咁做 唔係香港冇㗎嘞"},{"pid":"edf54be25691df85a8c6c5e90227f9e3e16faeac","tid":1708543,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4cHBEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4cHBEO.jpg&h=aaf225a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲有冇人記得10月1<br />\n根本有第一次就會有第二次<br />\n有第二次就會有第三次<br />\n遲早當街當巷殺死人<br />\n啲狗都唔需要負任何責任<br />\n覺得唔關自己事嗰啲人幾時先會醒啊<br />\n仲有落車拆rb屌人阻住你返工嘅人<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醒阿！港版64早已發生<br />\n無謂再呃自己出面一切正常</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cha6nZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcha6nZP.jpg&h=ffaebacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">之前山竹：</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4ViaBR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4ViaBR.jpg&h=c1033d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">今日香港：</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbH08nJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbH08nJ.png&h=acf9baee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hhRdJV4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhhRdJV4.